{
  "stem": "945.5",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so, one nice day, we marched into Czernowitz, the four of us, in our regs, our sacks, and again, we looked for a place where to put our-- where to find shelter.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And indeed, we did find an empty house.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he walked in there, and that's where we decided to make home.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, there were many people walking.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Many people.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we even ran into some young men that joined the Russian army and they, too, were walking.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was a mixture.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Everybody was moving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Everybody was moving.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We were going home.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Czernowitz wasn't our home, but it was near to our home.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, when we got to Czernowitz, we found out that in Vijnita, there is still a lot of strife going on, that there's still some hooligans hiding out in the forests and the Russians had trouble dealing with them.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we didn't go to Vijnita.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We stayed in Czernowitz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm going to make this short.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In Czernowitz, we settled in, and we tried-- from nothing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We started to be-- to bartering, to exchanging things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Then we got a-- a little-- a little place on the market where we would sell all different kinds of things that we were buying and selling.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And somehow we got ourselves into some more respectable clothes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We had food.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My dad got a job as a night watchman in a-- in a-- in a Russian military establishment, and a restaurant, and a store.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And things got better for us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "That lasted for about two years.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "After two years, the Russian authorities decided that any Romanian citizens that wanted to leave Russia would be free to do so.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Czernowitz was then in Russia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Czernowitz was-- Bukowina was occupied by the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "North Bukowina.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "North Bukowina.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
